# Practical Work 1: VPS Setup & Routing

## VPS Setup
- **Platform:** Google Cloud Platform
- **VM Name:** routing-vps
- **Machine Type:** f1-micro
- **OS:** Debian 11

## SSH Key Authentication
```bash
$ ssh -i ~/.ssh/vps-routing user@EXTERNAL_IP


